    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THIS GAME IS ABOUT CATLOAFS!</strong></h2>Tired of ordinary racing games? Then playing as a catloaf - slide, hiss, meow!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072190/extras/ff42cd2d434efbf2295df076c107d706.poster.avif?t=1722004154\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072190/extras/ff42cd2d434efbf2295df076c107d706.webm?t=1722004154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072190/extras/ff42cd2d434efbf2295df076c107d706.mp4?t=1722004154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THIS GAME IS NOT JUST ABOUT CATLOAFS!</strong></h2>Think this is yet another typical racing game? Wrong. We created a whole crazy system of fun game modes for each track. Race on ice, in fog, or jump into portals. And the best part - you can do it all with friends.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072190/extras/73a0e84ce8bdee2ef55412fbb4d0b1c3.poster.avif?t=1722004154\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072190/extras/73a0e84ce8bdee2ef55412fbb4d0b1c3.webm?t=1722004154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072190/extras/73a0e84ce8bdee2ef55412fbb4d0b1c3.mp4?t=1722004154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHOOSE YOUR CLASS AND PLAYSTYLE!</strong></h2>Catloaf Kart Racing allows you to build your own tactics before the race. Choose your class and use your special skills to hinder others or get you closer to the victory<br><br><strong>Our game will give you a truly unique gaming experience: both in terms of the setting and gameplay innovations - that you have never seen in this genre before!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072190/extras/7ffeaf3bee75adf9404b895bd4d61a5d.avif?t=1722004154\" width=616 height=250 /></span>",
